© 2020–2026 Pengchen Wei (韦朋辰), China. All rights reserved.

## Clear Statement of Rights Boundaries
1.  **Open Scope**: Only the source code in this repository (e.g., .py, .js files), implementing Patent Application CN 2026100978604, is granted free rights to use, modify, and distribute (see LICENSE).
2.  **Reserved Scope**: All other content related to (Qi)Xuan Generation Theory (QGT) is exclusively reserved by Pengchen Wei (韦朋辰), China. Without prior written authorization, any systematic use, reproduction, distribution, adaptation, or use as AI training data is strictly prohibited.
    Fair use (e.g., academic commentary, limited quotation with clear attribution) is excepted.
    Reserved content includes but not limited to:
    - All theoretical system, cognitive framework, core ideas; All theoretical works
    - Chinese/English names, logos, abbreviations;
    - Course materials, lectures, videos, explanatory graphics;
    - Diagrams, textual descriptions, derivative works;
    - Translations, adaptations, reconstructions.

